task.summary: Added LruCache and helper methods. Attempting to optimize performance by loading images in the background and implementing a disk cache.
Refactored code using Picasso. Deleted ThumbnailDownloader.
Finished Chapter 25 + Challenge: Polishing Your App Some More
Fixed bug: First page of images displayed twice
Implemented Context Menu for when a view is long pressed
Implemented "save image" method in context menu using http://stackoverflow.com/a/9397142/5677175
Implemented RetrieveImageTask and context menu in PhotoPageFragment.
Implemented "Enter fullscreen", "Copy link address", "Save Image", and "Share" features in PhotoPageFragment. Cleaned up a lot of code in this class and PhotoGalleryFragment.

Added a feature that prevents context menu item tasks "ie. saving, sharing an image" if the owner denies permission.
Implemented a "Share WebView Url" button in the action bar using ShareActionProvider and the sources:
http://developer.android.com/reference/android/widget/ShareActionProvider.html http://stackoverflow.com/questions/25093706/shareactionprovider-is-null
Implemented a Home/Up button for immediately returning to PhotoGalleryFragment after navigating through a few pages of the WebView in PhotoPageFragment
Added "sort" parameter to search results. Inputting a query now displays photos in sorted order via relevance.
Implemented and added a "Refresh" button to PhotoGalleryFragment
